Description: A white felt cat playfully hugging larger,brown felt Turkey. The cat has the white body with black details and pink nose. The turkey has the black dots design and white legs.

It features a cylindrical, brown felt body simulating a log, with distinctive white felted ends representing the cut surfaces of wood. Adding to its whimsical appeal, the ornament has a simple, endearing face with small, black embroidered eyes and two pink blush marks on its cheeks, giving it a friendly and cheerful character suitable for festive displays

These felt chocolate chip cookies are designed to realistically mimic their edible counterparts, crafted from soft, textured wool felt. Each cookie features a rounded, slightly domed shape in varying shades of tan and brown, adorned with scattered, darker brown "chocolate chips" applied to one surfac

It is divided into two distict color sections,a vibrant blue base and sunny yellow top adorned  with small orange polka dots that resembels as topping.The blue section displays a simple, hand needled face with black eyes and pink cheeks.
The main body is a rounded, light brown felt basket shape, holding the diffent shapes of fruits. There are red apple with green leaf, Orange with green leaf and purple grapes.

vibrant orange "pumpkin" slice crowned with a white whipped cream dollop, a rich red "cherry" slice featuring a delicate lattice crust, a dark brown "chocolate" slice adorned with a tiny white flower, and a lighter brown "apple" slice marked with decorative dark brown accents.

it features a plump, rounded brown body adorned with vibrant, multi-colored "feathers" in a classic autumn palette of oranges, yellows, and reds. Distinctive details include small black eyes, a cheerful yellow beak, and a prominent red wattle,

Each lollipop boasts a prominent round "candy" head characterized by a vibrant swirl pattern, created by carefully coiled and stitched strips of contrasting felt colors. One lollipop showcases a bright rainbow swirl of pink, yellow, blue, and green, while the other presents a harmonious blend of pink, purple, and white hues. The "candy" head is attached to a simple, cylindrical white felt stick, providing a clean and classic lollipop silhouette that is both tactile and visually appealing for pretend play or decorative purposes.

It is designed with meticulous attention to detail, showcasing a classic taco shell shape in a warm golden hue, stitched around the edges to give it a defined form and texture. Inside the shell, layers of vibrant green felt represent fresh lettuce, while red felt pieces depict juicy tomatoes, and brown felt for meat and cheese. A key distinguishing feature is the adorable embroidered face, complete with two small black eyes and a sweet, upturned smile in black thread,  enhanced with pink felt "blush" circles for added cuteness

it features a rounded, soft form with a simple handle and a small, brown-colored element on top, sauce. The most distinctive aspect of its design is the adorable, embroidered "smiley face" with small, dark eyes and blush-pink cheeks, imbuing the object with a friendly and cute, "kawaii" aesthetic
It has the shape of halved avocado, complete with the bright, ligher green inner and darker green outer skin. A rounded brown pit is securely integrated into the center.
The design of each piece mimics a layered chocolate cake with a dollop of white frosting and a red cherry on top. The red cherry is a small, solid red sphere, with tiny stem.

The harvested corn is crafted with the soft felt using needle felting technique. The design featues a yellow corn kernel section with scattered orange dot representing each kernel, all framed by the green felt husk that partially wraps around the sides.

The avocado set is the pair of avocado halves crafted with soft green wool.  Each piece is designed in avocado half, featuring a lime green inner flesh with dark green outside. One half has a empty circular part where the seed should be and another half has the dark brown seed. Both halves has the black needed eyes and black smiling mouth. It is about 7cm in length.
The main body is wet felted. A lighter, off white oval patch on the belly, a black, nose, a round eyes and ears.
The base is wet felted. It is shaped as the conversation bubble with the triangular point at the buttom.
The figures are styled as a groom in a dark suit and a bride in a white dress decorated with pink stitched accents, holding a small pink flower
Cupcake featues the teal felt base with stitched white stripes and a cream-colored label decorated with two tiny pink embroidered hearts. The top is a fluffy swril of bright pink felt frosting.
Roses are crafted with the soft wet felted wool. It beautifully layered the petals to resemble as blossoms.
It features the set of love letters and messages, designed with charming details in red and white. The main base primarily wet felted with the white wool. It has the red stitched around the edges.
The base is crafted with soft wool. It has the shape of the heart. It featues the white needled conversation on the top.

The heart shaped potion bottle constructed with the layered felt and visible stitching. The bottle has a peach color and a rounded, heart shape on the main body, topped with the small neck and tiny tan cork secured with stitching. The design focuses on the bottle featuring two hearts, a pink outer heart and smaller darker pink heart. The length is 5cm and breadth is 5cm.
